extendedInfo.description: Mobile Money is a convenient way to access your account when you are on the go. Enjoy money management at full force with the Collins Community Credit Union (CCCU) mobile app.Features:- Check Account Balances- View recent transactions- Transfer money between accounts- Pay bills Keywords: Banking, Finance, CCCU, Collins Community Credit Union, Credit Union, Iowa, Bill Pay

reviews.title: Security Should be #1 for Personal Finance Apps
reviews.comment: I have followed several versions of this App and it continues to be incompatible with password manager Apps... cannot paste-in username and password from the phone clipboard. This serious failing makes the CCCU App a non-starter. I won\'t even try it without this important feature. Why should we have to type in memorized or \"on paper\" simple usernames and passwords??  Fiserv should be ashamed to be producing Apps that do not promote use of complex passwords and even complex login names.  Samsung Galaxy Note II with Android 4.1.2.
reviews.author: Robert Van Horn

reviews.title: Love the CCCU Mobile App
reviews.comment: I recently became a member of CCCU and immediately downloaded the mobile app.  I love being able to look at my account balances and transaction history on the go!  Once you have logged into your account you can view account balances, transfer money and make payments.  There is a new popmoney feature which allows you to transfer money directly into another person\342\200\231s account.  The app is easy to use, and the best part\342\200\246 it\342\200\231s FREE!
reviews.author: Taylor Yezek
